iv><div class="TintOverlay TintOverlay--dark TintOverlay--tint TintOverlay--tint-high"></div></div></div><div class="GeneralContainer"><div id="2be7023d-f45b-45e7-bf07-8b5edd98c97b" class="StackModule"><div class="TextModule__Container TextModule__Container--dark"><div class="TextModule container--hub TextModule--dark"><div class="TextModule__Content"><div class="TextModule__Content__Inside"><div class="TextModule__Content__Heading TextModule__Content__Heading--allCaps TextModule__Content__Heading--noText">EARTH MONTH 2026</div><div class="TextModule__Content__Source"><span class="RichText">Learn how to explore the natural wonders found in your backyard—and put your new knowledge to the test with a series of short quizzes. <a href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/environment/topic/wonder-lessons">See more here.</a></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="OneUpPromo"><div class="OneUpPromo__Body"><div class="OneUpPromo__Body--Content"><div class="OneUpPromoCard__Content OneUpPromoCard__Content--dark OneUpPromoCard__Content--left"><a class="AnchorLink AnchorLink--dark OneUpPromoCard__Content__AnchorLink OneUpPromoCard__Content__AnchorLink--dark" tabindex="0" aria-label="Learn to spot cumulonimbus clouds" href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/environment/article/wonder-lessons-cloud-spotting-guide-cumulonimbus"></a><div class="Card__Content__ImageWrapper"><div class="Card__Content__Image--img"><figure class="Image aspect-ratio--parent Card__Content__Image--img"><div class="RatioFrame aspect-ratio--auto"></div><div class="Image__Wrapper Image__Wrapper--relative"><picture><source srcSet="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" media="(max-width: 320px)"/><source srcSet="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" media="(max-width: 383px)"/><source srcSet="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" media="(max-width: 522px)"/><source srcSet