 2016 shows a satellite-to-earth link established between quantum satellite \"Micius\" and the quantum teleportation experiment platform in Ali, southwest China's Tibet Autonomous Region.","ttl":"h_11.01779862"},"abstract":"We may never beam ourselves off the planet. But quantum teleportation is poised to bring about a new era of computing—and revolutionize our understanding of the subatomic world.","title":"Teleportation is no longer just science fiction—at the quantum level","tags":[{"name":"Audio: 9 min listen","id":"_none","type":"custom"}],"abTest":{"testId":"ng_pw_copy-287","variantId":"variant_a-1126","type":"paywallTest","variant":"variant_a","abTest":"ng_pw_copy-287*variant_a-1126"}},{"id":"f7a68b17-1f81-4472-9b6f-ac4a61186e58","cmsType":"RegularStandardPrismTile","isPremium":false,"isEntitled":false,"isUserAuthed":false,"pageType":"home","description":"These bold thinkers believe our world needs imaginative solutions and urgent action—and are leading the charge for change.","aspectRatio":"3x2","ctas":[{"url":"https://www.nationalgeographic.com/culture/nat-geo-33/graphics/2026","text":"natgeo.ctaText.explore","icon":"interactive"}],"img":{"crps":[{"nm":"raw","aspRto":1.9047619047619047,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd103d5-7a19-4b12-ab95-50502aab84ed/NG33-2026_OG.jpg"},{"nm":"16x9","aspRto":1.7777777777777777,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd103d5-7a19-4b12-ab95-50502aab84ed/NG33-2026_OG_16x9.jpg"},{"nm":"3x2","aspRto":1.5,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd103d5-7a19-4b12-ab95-50502aab84ed/NG33-2026_OG_3x2.jpg"},{"nm":"square","aspRto":1,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd103d5-7a19-4b12-ab95-50502aab84ed/NG33-2026_OG_square.jpg"},{"nm":"2x3","aspRto":0.6666666666666666,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd103d5-7a19-4b12-ab95-50502aab84ed/NG33-2026_OG_2x3.jpg"},{"nm":"3x4","aspRto":0.75,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd103d5-7a19-4b12-ab95-50502aab84ed/NG33-2026_OG_3x4.jpg"},{"nm":"4x3","aspRto":1.3333333333333333,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/8bd1