l Ramsey is an entomologist and National Geographic 2022 Wayfinder Awardee. Ramsey’s research on the decline of honey bees has taken him around the globe to better understand how pollinator pandemics start – and how they can be stopped.","ttl":"NG Asset Sammy Ramsey"},"abstract":"The singing entomologist’s journey teaches us about the power of a unique perspective.","title":"How Sammy Ramsey redefines the mission to save bees","abTest":{"testId":"ng_pw_copy-287","variantId":"variant_a-1126","type":"paywallTest","variant":"variant_a","abTest":"ng_pw_copy-287*variant_a-1126"}},{"id":"4aadb903-eb8b-4374-af26-4372f8cd3295","cmsType":"RegularStandardPrismTile","isPremium":false,"isEntitled":false,"isUserAuthed":false,"pageType":"home","storyId":"drn:src:natgeo:unison::prod:13557daf-ec96-4efd-9c10-86c30609026a","cId":"4aadb903-eb8b-4374-af26-4372f8cd3295_13557daf-ec96-4efd-9c10-86c30609026a","description":"The researcher and National Geographic Explorer is helping uncover how bees’ environments shape their smarts.","ctas":[{"url":"https://www.nationalgeographic.com/impact/article/felicity-muth-explorer-story","text":"natgeo.ctaText.read","icon":"article"}],"img":{"crps":[{"nm":"raw","aspRto":1.499267935578331,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/14ebaadf-4d88-47c4-9670-276683bad237/NGS2025EXPL_FelicityMuth_CR_MarkThiessen_1369.jpg"},{"nm":"16x9","aspRto":1.7777777777777777,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/14ebaadf-4d88-47c4-9670-276683bad237/NGS2025EXPL_FelicityMuth_CR_MarkThiessen_1369_16x9.jpg"},{"nm":"3x2","aspRto":1.5,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/14ebaadf-4d88-47c4-9670-276683bad237/NGS2025EXPL_FelicityMuth_CR_MarkThiessen_1369_3x2.jpg"},{"nm":"square","aspRto":1,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/14ebaadf-4d88-47c4-9670-276683bad237/NGS2025EXPL_FelicityMuth_CR_MarkThiessen_1369_square.jpg"},{"nm":"2x3","aspRto":0.6666666666666666,"url":"https://i.natgeofe.com/n/14ebaadf-4d88-47c4-9670-276683bad237/NGS2025EXPL_FelicityMuth_CR_MarkThiessen_1369_2x3.jpg"},{"nm":"3x4","aspRto"